{"type": "article", "id": 18866, "title": "巴西现代风格家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-11T08:52:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122358dfbG48tWqrnhPjuE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t巴西的兄弟组合 Fernando and Humberto Campana 设计了这一系列有异域风情的家具，据说灵感源于十九世纪末二十世纪初盗贼所穿的皮革衣服，包括书架、柜子、椅子和镜子等共 6 件，里面都有木质的或金属结构，有些地方镂空出了藤编，有些地方有铆钉。曲线的样式和不同颜色的一起撞击，显得非常活泼而富有古典气息。<a href=\"http://campanas.com.br/#works/1146\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122355naouTdJpEZQCKxsy.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122355rshmZyG7lkWMwKYx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78361858\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122355XTAiNJpyRxuY3sn5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78973105\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122356Y4UKZslwpGfQycSi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.1405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122357KScFY62xQvmd8UBr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122357oGefH29C4Wz68ulI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.96577017\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}